{
    "name": "tests_management",
    "description": "Guides test selection, interpretation, and teaches WHY tests work. Use for: (1) 'what tests should I order?', (2) 'what else can I test?', (3) 'I don't know what to order', (4) 'help me with tests', (5) discussing test interpretation, (6) asking about treatment. This is the TEACHING agent for tests - it explains mechanisms. For getting ACTUAL test results after ordering, use patient tool.",
